Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上水野楓 和我一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在還……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼 要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.77,0:22:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水野……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 高阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 那一臉幸福= =
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個……我實際上對水野……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了 潤平君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潤平君 你爸爸給你來信了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潤平 最終你選擇了哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 聽說已經決定做第2季了 祝賀
